Package org.dockbox.selene.core.annotations.event.processing

  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    SkipIf.Type  
  • Annotation Types Summary 
    Annotation Type Description
    Getter
    Tries to obtain the value of a given (getter) method, or null for any parameter but event.
    Provided
    Tries to get the instance of the type through InjectableBootstrap.getInstance(java.lang.Class<T>, org.dockbox.selene.core.server.properties.InjectorProperty<?>...).
    SkipIf
    Skips the event listener if the given parameter is one of the possible types (null, zero, or empty).
    UnwrapOrSkip
    Attempts to unwrap the final object if it is a instance of Exceptional or Optional.
    WrapSafe
    Wraps the parameter in a Exceptional instance, unless the parameter is the event.
